    <node id="source5.Consumer_Profiles">
      <data key="d0">source5.Consumer_Profiles</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The Consumer_Profiles.csv table contains personal and financial details of consumers, including unique AgencyID, names, net worth, employer, number of credit cards, marital status, gender, phone number, number of children, age, address, country, number of cars, middle initial, and postal code. Numeric fields are stored as strings or floats.&lt;SEP&gt;source5.Consumer_Profiles is a CSV table containing personal and financial details of consumers, as described in the input text, with columns for identifiers, demographics, financial information, and contact details.</data>
